'''Sunnis''', called the '''Princess of Good Earth Creatures''', the '''True Stone''', and the '''Lode Mother''', was the good [[archomental]] of the [[Elemental Plane of Earth]], and thus was the opposite and nemesis of [[Ogrémoch]]. Her symbol was an hourglass with sand trickling downward.
{{Quote|I mean very little. Ogrémoch's death means much.|Sunnis}}
